    "page_range": "16-1",
    "summary": "This section provides a market analysis and ranked dataset for the 2025 overseas mobile game industry. It is structured to answer retrieval queries on the following dimensions:\n- **Topics & Scope:** Global mobile game revenue trends, comparative success strategies for legacy versus new titles, and 2025 market performance.\n- **Entities & Dates:** Centers on 2025 annual data. Key entities include Supercell, 《皇室战争》(Clash Royale), 《奔奔王国》(Kingshot), and the full TOP 30 game roster. Data is attributed to 点点数据.\n- **Claims & Insights:** Asserts that in a saturated market, legacy game revival depends on deep, risk-tolerant reconstruction of core progression, gameplay, and economic systems. New product breakthroughs rely on precise micro-innovations on validated models combined with saturated marketing campaigns. Identifies 《奔奔王国》 as the only new release to enter the 2025 TOP 30.\n- **Metrics & Table:** Contains the \"2025年海外移动游戏收入TOP30\" table, mapping Rank (1–30), Game Name, and Annual Revenue (全年流水 in 亿元). Notable metrics include #1 Last War: Survival (154.53亿元), #13 皇室战争 (46.40亿元), and #17 奔奔王国 (42.26亿元).\n- **Evidence Types:** Structured revenue ranking table, analytical market commentary, and source attribution. Includes a forward reference indicating detailed case studies for the two highlighted titles appear on the subsequent page.\n- **Retrieval Questions Answered:** What were the top-grossing overseas mobile games in 2025 and their exact annual revenues? Which new titles broke into the annual top 30? How do growth strategies differ between revitalized legacy games and new launches? What is the 2025 revenue performance of Supercell's featured titles? What organization sourced and compiled the ranking data?"
